body: Yes, it shows as U, which means undefined. I'd need to check later, but I'm guessing that the script failed to define the symbol. Could you bazel clean, to be sure? See what happens to the `tf_version_info_generate`. It's supposed to put something in `bazel-genfiles/tensorflow/util/version_info.cc`. That should have the git version in there. If it's there, check the lib file and so on.
